    %% External flows
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token"| K8sAPI
    User -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Edge/Reencrypt"| Route
    MLApp -->|"gRPC/80 or 443<br/>TLS (if configured)<br/>K8s RBAC / OIDC"| Services

    %% Operator flows
    K8sAPI -->|"Watch Events<br/>SA Token"| Operator
