    Online -->|"TCP/5432<br/>TLS optional<br/>Secret"| PostgreSQL
    Offline -->|"TCP/5432<br/>TLS optional<br/>Secret"| PostgreSQL
    Registry -->|"TCP/5432<br/>TLS optional<br/>Secret"| PostgreSQL
